  "relationship": "Continuing relationship from previous interactions.",
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "我有时候想，为什么绝大多数人心中都有一个大体类似的理想社会，可理想社会的逻辑却与现实逻辑如此冲突",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "这是因事而发，还是突然感叹？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "这样的事每天每刻都要面对。今天在会议上，面对投资人和同事的脸，会觉得执着于理想社会真是天真幼稚的幻想。离开了那个环境，又觉得是方才的自己狭隘",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "今天理想社会的哪个角落被现实击打了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "制药卖药，盈利和治病。都是老生常谈了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "懂了，太具体的不能说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "马克思他老人家有言了，资本主义社会它就是这样子。何况你去的还是资本主义老巢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "哈哈这个说法",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "话说英国也有很厉害的制药公司吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "跨国公司，正好这边有跟我们合作的负责人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "真厉害",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "谁？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "都挺厉害。你这年纪轻轻担负大任，这公司不知道多少年积累成跨国医药资本",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "医药公司能开这么多年确实厉害，不过不是那几家医药巨头，是小规模非高精尖公司，没有研发部门的那种",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "类推下来，我很厉害，但也没到那么厉害",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是资料属实，以你的年纪是相当厉害了。给往后的人生留点进步空间吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "抬举抬举",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "你喜欢诗歌吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "还行。什么诗派",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "城市牧歌诗派",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "还有这个诗派啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有。我乱起的名字",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "Earth has not anything to show more fair:\nDull would he be of soul who could pass by",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "A sight so touching in its majesty:\nThis City now doth, like a garment, wear\nThe beauty of the morning; silent, bare,\nShips, towers, domes, theatres, and temples lie\nOpen unto the fields, and to the sky",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "All bright and glittering in the smokeless air.\nNever did sun more beautifully steep",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "In his first splendour, valley, rock, or hill;\nNe'er saw I, never felt, a calm so deep!",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "The river glideth at his own sweet will:",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "Dear God! the very houses seem asleep;\nAnd all that mighty heart is lying still!",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "哇哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "哇哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "公交上有人突然站起来念诗，念的就是这一首",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "也许是专门为游客安排的节目",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "真怪浪漫的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "和你分享",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    }
  ],
